"{\"uid\": \"globalnews.ca-news-10645575-paris-2024-olympics-mascot-what-is-a-phryges\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Instructions: Want to discuss?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 31, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Instructions\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 12}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please read ourCommenting Policyfirst.\", \"from\": 32, \"to\": 70, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourCommenting Policyfirst\", \"from\": 44, \"to\": 69}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you get Global News from Instagram or Facebook - that will be changing.Find out how you can still connect with us.\", \"from\": 72, \"to\": 189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 83, \"end\": 94, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Global_News\", \"score\": 0.9999992524033653, \"rank\": 7.475969805738691e-07, \"text\": \"Global News\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Global_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Global_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Instagram\", \"from\": 100, \"to\": 109}, {\"ngram\": \"Facebook\", \"from\": 113, \"to\": 121}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 186, \"to\": 188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The2024 Paris Olympicsare finally upon us, and there is one pretty prominent symbol for these games that has a lot of people scratching their heads.\", \"from\": 191, \"to\": 339, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 199, \"end\": 204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6529529166060228e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The2024\", \"from\": 191, \"to\": 198}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 232}, {\"ngram\": \"one pretty prominent symbol\", \"from\": 247, \"to\": 274}, {\"ngram\": \"these games\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 290}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 305}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 315}, {\"ngram\": \"their heads\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two red blobs that make up this year's iteration of the Summer Olympics'mascotslook more like they belong in a geometry class than on a sporting field, but they are actually a pretty important part of French history.\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 546, \"end\": 560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French history\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The two red blobs\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 358}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's iteration\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 393}, {\"ngram\": \"the Summer\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 407}, {\"ngram\": \"a geometry class\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 470}, {\"ngram\": \"a sporting field\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 495}, {\"ngram\": \"a pretty important part\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No, thePhryges, as they are called, are not a pair of triangles, nor are they tongues or any other part of the body - instead, they are meant to represent a pair of Phrygian caps, a type of hat that is symbolic of the French liberation.\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 799, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 728, \"end\": 736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\", \"score\": 0.9999999607985054, \"rank\": 3.9201541692170236e-08, \"text\": \"Phrygian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\"}, {\"begin\": 781, \"end\": 787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9992917155442002, \"rank\": 0.0007084773264937387, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pair\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"triangles\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"tongues\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"any other part\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"a pair\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 724}, {\"ngram\": \"a type\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"hat\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On vous pr\\u00e9sente la Phryge Olympique et la Phryge Paralympique !Les mascottes de#Paris2024\\u2728Sportives, f\\u00eatardes\\u2026 et fran\\u00e7aises \\ud83c\\uddeb\\ud83c\\uddf7 Here are the Olympic Phryge and the Paralympic Phryge!The#Paris2024mascots \\u2728They are sporty, love to party\\u2026 and are so French \\ud83c\\uddeb\\ud83c\\uddf7pic.twitter.com/plupKzQqNs - Paris 2024 (@Paris2024)November 14, 2022 The Phryges(pronounced FREE-juh) are based on caps worn by 18th-century French revolutionaries who wore the head coverings as a symbol of freedom, but according to National Geographic, the origin of the capgoes back thousands of years, appearing in the Trojan War.\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1052, \"end\": 1058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9992917155442002, \"rank\": 0.0007084773264937387, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1209, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Revolution\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French revolutionaries\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Revolution\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Revolution\"}, {\"begin\": 1301, \"end\": 1320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Geographic\", \"score\": 0.9941780857625857, \"rank\": 0.0058560074