"ngram\": \"The fact\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1736}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics mascot\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1764}, {\"ngram\": \"a visible disability\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1789}, {\"ngram\": \"a strong message\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The caps, he added, are on \\\"a mission of revolution through sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1910, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The caps\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1851}, {\"ngram\": \"a mission\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1880}, {\"ngram\": \"revolution\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1894}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout French history, the caps have been worn.\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1927, \"end\": 1941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French history\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They were donned when French revolutionaries stormed the Bastille prison in 1789, marking the beginning of the French Revolution during the construction of the Eiffel Tower and Notre-Dame de Paris Cathedral, and even at early iterations of the Olympic games.\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1990, \"end\": 2012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Revolution\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French revolutionaries\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Revolution\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Revolution\"}, {\"begin\": 2025, \"end\": 2033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Storming_of_the_Bastille\", \"score\": 0.9968463814762426, \"rank\": 0.0031635952961230128, \"text\": \"Bastille\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Storming_of_the_Bastille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Storming_of_the_Bastille\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2067}, {\"ngram\": \"the French Revolution\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2092}, {\"ngram\": \"the construction\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2116}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"Notre-Dame de Paris Cathedral\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"early iterations\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2200}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic games\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Phryge and the Paralympic Phryge are taking the lead of a tribe which always has its trainers on \\ud83d\\udc5fWhat could be better than little Phrygian caps to lead the revolution through sport and accompany us to the#Paris2024Games!pic.twitter.com/hUjFI09zZM - Paris 2024 (@Paris2024)November 14, 2022 Even today, Phrygian caps find their place in French art and society, being worn by protestors, appearing on French stamps and currency, and appearing in a part of the country's national school curriculum.\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2212, \"end\": 2225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999429401231, \"rank\": 4.8240330383016017e-08, \"text\": \"Olympic games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 2372, \"end\": 2380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\", \"score\": 0.9999999607985054, \"rank\": 3.9201541692170236e-08, \"text\": \"Phrygian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\"}, {\"begin\": 2548, \"end\": 2556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\", \"score\": 0.9999999607985054, \"rank\": 3.9201541692170236e-08, \"text\": \"Phrygian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\"}, {\"begin\": 2582, \"end\": 2588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9992917155442002, \"rank\": 0.0007084773264937387, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2645, \"end\": 2651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9992917155442002, \"rank\": 0.0007084773264937387, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paralympic Phryge\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2288}, {\"ngram\": \"a tribe\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2299}, {\"ngram\": \"its trainers\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2329}, {\"ngram\": \"the revolution\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2403}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2417}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2434}, {\"ngram\": \"the#Paris2024Games!pic.twitter.com/hUjFI09zZM - Paris\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2491}, {\"ngram\": \"(@Paris2024)November\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2517}, {\"ngram\": \"their place\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2569}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2595}, {\"ngram\": \"protestors\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2621}, {\"ngram\": \"currency\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2662}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2687}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's national school curriculum\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organizers have described the Olympic and Paralympic Phryges as belonging to a larger family.\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2831, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organizers\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2748}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic and Paralympic Phryges\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2798}, {\"ngram\": \"a larger family\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are thetwo main characters in a large tribe; they are part of the family of Phryges,\\\" Paris 2024 brand director Julie Matikhine said, according to Olympics.com.\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2991, \"end\": 3003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999981398335896, \"rank\": 1.8601699084331831e-06, \"text\": \"Olympics.com\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thetwo main characters\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2865}, {\"ngram\": \"a large tribe\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2882}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2897}, {\"ngram\": \"the family\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2911}, {\"ngram\": \"Phryges\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 2922}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris 2024 brand director Julie Matikhine\", \"from\": 2925, \"to\": 2966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"According to our narrative, they have existed for thousands of years and were present during several key events in French history.\\\"\", \"from\": 3000, \"to\": 3132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3121, \"end\": 3135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French history\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our narrative\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3027}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 3051, \"to\": 3060}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 3064, \"to\": 3069}, {\"ngram\": \"several key events\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She continued: \\\"Now they have returned for this big event in France to lead a mission of revolution through sport.\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3200, \"end\": 3206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999996532547503, \"rank\": 3.1569132007774096e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this big event\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3191}, {\"ngram\": \"a mission\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3219}, {\"ngram\": \"revolution\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3233}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3242, \"to\": 3247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The aim is to show that sport can change everything in society.\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3312, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The aim\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3256}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3273, \"to\": 3278}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3290, \"to\": 3300}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The objective is to show that sport and its values can do great things.\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3384, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The objective\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3326}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3343, \"to\": 3348}, {\"ngram\": \"its values\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3363}, {\"ngram\": \"great things\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about fraternity, solidarity and it helps society grow.\\\"\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3446, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fraternity\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3406}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And while the two mascots look quite similar, they have been assigned opposite but complementary personalities.\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3559, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the two mascots\", \"from\": 3458, \"to\": 3473}, {\"ngram\": \"opposite but complementary personalities\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Phryge \\\"is a tactician with a calculating, mathematical brain.\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3635, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Phryge\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3579}, {\"ngram\": \"a tactician\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3595}, {\"ngram\": \"a calculating, mathematical brain\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its methodical mind and alluring charm are sure to inspire people to get involved with sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 3636, \"to\": 3730, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Its methodical mind\", \"from\": 3636, \"to\": 3655}, {\"ngram\": \"alluring charm\", \"from\": 3660, \"to\": 3674}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3695, \"to\": 3701}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3723, \"to\": 3728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the Paralympic Phryge, who has a prosthetic leg and racing blade, \\\"is spontaneous and full of energy and enthusiasm.\\\"\", \"from\": 3731, \"to\": 3859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paralympic Phryge\", \"from\": 3742, \"to\": 3763}, {\"ngram\": \"a prosthetic leg\", \"from\": 3773, \"to\": 3789}, {\"ngram\": \"racing blade\", \"from\": 3794, \"to\": 3806}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 3836, \"to\": 3842}, {\"ngram\": \"enthusiasm\", \"from\": 3847, \"to\": 3857}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Together, their motto is: \\\"Alone we go faster, but together we go further.\\\"\", \"from\": 3861, \"to\": 3936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their motto\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 3882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The email you need for the day's top news stories from Canada and around the world.\", \"from\": 3938, \"to\": 4021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3998, \"end\": 4004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999919446069484, \"rank\": 5.355458305543495e-06, \"text